e. (~3h) → deps: T-001\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- **T-035** [T1] Refactor composition stage to emit score-tree with PerformanceIntent + SectionEnvelope + IntentTag metadata, deterministic from composition seed. (~3h) → deps: T-001\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- **T-036** [T1] Define the OSC/SuperCollider event contract that carries full Event metadata including rule_stack provenance through to the synth. (~3h) → deps: T-001\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- **T-037** [T1] Build a deterministic replay harness that reproduces any past performance from (score, composition_seed, interpretation_seed, delta_track). (~3h) → deps: T-001\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-*Subtotal: ~24 hours*\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+*Subtotal: ~27 hours*\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n ### Sprint 6: Stretch Goals\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n **Depends on:** Sprint 0 (Versioning System)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-- **T-021** [T2] Add post-tonal, spectral, and microtonal material strategies. (~6h)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-- **T-022** [T2] Build SuperCollider recipe references without coupling tests to live audio. (~6h)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-- **T-023** [T2] Add course-driven self-critique and revision targets. (~6h)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-- **T-024** [T2] Turn the production course into executable curriculum exercises. (~6h)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-- **T-025** [T2] Add operator diagnostics for production-course decisions. (~6h)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- **T-038** [T2] Couple narrative engine to SectionEnvelope selection so dramatic arcs drive section choice. (~6h)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- **T-039** [T2] Build audio-rendered SSM + Foote novelty cross-check via librosa on the actual rendered audio. (~6h)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- **T-040** [T2] Establish listener-review workflow: weekly rendered pieces tagged with rule-stack provenance, ablation tooling documented for operators, review log template in place. (~6h)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-*Subtotal: ~30 hours*\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+*Subtotal: ~18 hours*\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n ---\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n 